## 7. Performance Considerations

### Time Complexity
- **Push (append)**: O(1) - Constant time
- **Pop**: O(1) - Constant time  
- **Peek (stack[-1])**: O(1) - Constant time
- **Empty Check**: O(1) - Constant time

### Space Complexity
- **Space**: O(n) where n is number of items in stack
- **Auxiliary Space**: O(1) for basic operations

### Memory Efficiency
